{"tid":2093651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「加速主義」APPLE停止更新中國區的遊戲","createTime":"2020-07-04T04:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T04:09:10.000Z","uid":184099,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb4341b8fecfe44258d7fb81ac4283d8c4c4e85","tid":2093651,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4343577/2020-07-02/news-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8BApp+Store%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/?variant=zh-hk&amp;appedition=vancouver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4343577%2F2020-07-02%2Fnews-%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258BApp%2BStore%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk%26appedition%3Dvancouver&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=a8bccbf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/4343577/2020-07-02/news-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8BApp+Store%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/?variant=zh-hk&amp;appedition=vancouver</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中美關係持續緊張，英國「金融時報」（The Financial Times）報導，指蘋果公司（Apple）暫停中國App Store上萬個iPhone遊戲更新。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國蘋果今日告訴遊戲開發商，如果開發者想上架特定遊戲到中國App Store，如今需要取得中國當局許可。</span></strong>報道引述Appin China的數據，指中國App Store目前約有6萬個付費或應用程式內購買的手機遊戲。然而，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從2010年至今，中國監管機構僅發放約4.3萬個許可證，2019年更只發出1570個，</span></strong>有數千個遊戲不符合新規定。開發人員2月時被告知，6月30日前必須遵守中國手機遊戲法律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國於2016年推出規定，要求遊戲開發商需先取得監管機構頒發的證照，才能在中國發行付費或應用程式內付費的內容。中國目前是全球最大的遊戲市場，占蘋果一大部分的營收來源。<br />\n<br />\n根據遊戲、電競和手遊研究公司Newzoo，預期今年中國市場占iOS手遊總營收53%，相當於130億美元左右。市場調查機構Sensor Tower指出，預計中國App Store年銷售額達164億美元，高於美國市場的154億美元。"},{"pid":"c03ffb9b6f717347486c8150d63ee2090dc81034","tid":2093651,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d378a854d4c9a189b2a098e17cf07360b8198f8","tid":2093651,"uid":88812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:03:27.000Z","msg":"做乜勁?篇文話中國唔畀過。唔係apple唔更新喎"},{"pid":"3d8b2a4e9a103514e1fc8531a273bfdde85a5e49","tid":2093651,"uid":160550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"不怕 還有華為鴻蒙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7859e6dfeb17a485410d48f22cdfb8f92f5b73","tid":2093651,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d378a854d4c9a189b2a098e17cf07360b8198f8","tid":2093651,"uid":88812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:03:27.000Z","msg":"做乜勁?篇文話中國唔畀過。唔係apple唔更新喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"所以味話加速"}]}